        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Don't exceed 4–5 boxes high when stacking. Distribute weight evenly to prevent crushing. Place heavier boxes on the bottom and lighter items on top.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Store in Cool, Dry Locations</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Moisture damages cardboard. Keep boxes away from damp areas like unventilated basements or near water pipes. Climate-controlled spaces are ideal for long-term storage.</p>

